text: The President of the Regional Government of Galicia (, ), is the head of government of Galicia. The president leads the executive branch of the regional government. The current office is established under the Galician Statute of Autonomy. It is occupied by Alberto Núñez Feijóo. ==See also== *Xunta de Galicia *Politics of Galicia *List of Presidents of the Regional Government of Galicia ==References==
title: President of the Regional Government of Galicia
